{"tid":2410641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸反政變示威強調：無大台","createTime":"2021-02-16T19:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T19:42:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"59a32f5f4c870e1a613e30bbf0370b4f21411b2f","tid":2410641,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T19:42:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4765562/2021-02-10/post-%e7%b7%ac%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e4%bb%bf%e6%95%88%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af-強調無大台/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4765562%2F2021-02-10%2Fpost-%25e7%25b7%25ac%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e4%25bb%25bf%25e6%2595%2588%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E7%84%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%B0%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6b2e7875\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4765562/2021-02-10/post-%e7%b7%ac%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e4%bb%bf%e6%95%88%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af-強調無大台/</a><br />\n<br />\n美聯社引述社運人士稱，緬甸的反政變示威活動沒有大台。著名社運人士欣沙順雷伊說：「這項運動是沒有領袖的，人們以自己的方式和意願走上街頭。」緬甸各地的社運組織、專業團體、工會及個人紛紛上街反對政變。示威者傳遞宣傳單張，教導如何使用加密通訊，以及如何在抗議期間自保安全等，部分資料源於香港的示威。"}]}